The rules of any roleplaying game should be a basis for resolving those
bits which are NOT "Role Played". By by that standard, the rest of the
followingg makes little sense...

>But I\'ve used the Traveller universe conntinually, right now we\'re doing a
>hybrid of Jovian Chronicles*  and T2300, as the Pluto research station
>finally finish building the first stuterwarp craft, and take the untested
>ship out into instellar space to avoid it being captured by an Earther
>strike force...
