You just reminded me of an *old* TV show that could easily be
translated into Traveller, especially in the Spinward Marches during
one of the Frontier Wars, or maybe in the Solomani Rim.

Better yet, make it in a sector that gets occasional Vargr or Aslan
incursions. Nothing *really* serious, but enough to require *some* sort
