Exactly why there is a traveller world that is fun to game in.
Detroit is a city that, at the same time that it\'s main employers moved out, 
also became ruled by an ethnic group that had been picked on in the past and 
decided to take the following actions [just after open warfare broke out, 
requiring tanks and machine guns to restore some level of peace]:
1) Kick the other [usual majority] racial group out
2) Intentionally dis-empower the police force by hiring unqualifed and/or 
criminal police
3) Rule the local court system with judges and jurys who would allow many of 
their ethnic group to go free, or serve little time
4) Fail to repair battle damage [the \'broken windows\' theory of the criminal 
