the gravity fails. A Cutlass, being one-handed, and having the half-basket,
allows one to use the other hand for a hold (On opponent or on wall). Being
a slashing and a mass weapon, and having a sharp point, it can rip/puncture
vacc suits, crush through soft armors, and cut exposed flesh; additionally,
a cutlass, being curved, requires less swing room than an equivalent
mass/pen straight bladed sword.


