decide that it was too dangerous for a minor power to
have whatever weapon it was, and would take whatever
steps were necessary to restore the status quo.  

Finally, remember that any fleet of ships probably has
enough nuclear missiles and spinal weapons to destroy
a star system\'s civilization nearly as completely as
destroying the planets themselves -- especially from
the perspective of the residents.  Dead is dead, after
all.

