    'body' => 'In mail you write:

>>I know of no law - In the US at least - that restricts any private
>>individual
>>(or corporation for that matter) from engaging in space launch.
>>The reasons "private enterprise" hasn\'t gotten into the space game
>>on a free lance basis is that nobody can figure out how to do it
