universes I am NOT writing only leads me to create characters that I then
have to spend a long time figuring out how to import back into my own
universe, which is very frustrating.  Since I also believe that magick and
technology are both applied sciences we don\'t always understand, this
makes life interesting.  I used psionics rather a lot and invented whole
bunches of powers.

