the sector it was in being mostly "dead" or damaged worlds due to the
supernova that created the black hole. As I recall, being within a
dozen parsecs of a supernova would be *really* bad news for your planet.

There\'d also be this rather noticeable nebula (the expanding gases from
the supernova) filling most of the sector. 

