to fill out the ranks. The book has some cool tales of using rifles to drive 
off white forces drive-by attacks, he trained his defense troops to judge 
their fire by watching for the flashes when the rounds hit the cars. They 
also used rifle fire to drive off a small plane which they had been warned 
was on a bombing mission against their headquarters house. They later held a 
white couple for either racial dislike of whites or to save their lives, and 
the Feds got involved, decided that the nazi rifles meant they were bad 
people, and the leader was forced to flee to Cuba. Along the way the national 
